		<td><b>How well can Metal Slug backgrounds be recreated with tiles?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I do know that Metal Slug and it's sequels DO in fact occasionally recycle BG tiles (yes, I know they're actually sprites  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_rolleyes.gif" alt=":roll:" title="Rolling Eyes" /> ), but not nearly as much as SNES and MD/Genesis games.  I want to know how much you can replicate using half or less as many unique tiles.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


