		<td><b>Re: How well can Metal Slug backgrounds be recreated with ti</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For what reason? Backgrounds from Metal Slug probably reuse more tiles than you would think, as they are often placed far away and/or surrounded by other unique tiles. Less than halving the number of tiles will almost guarantee it to look like shit, imo.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


