		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The backgrounds never overlap, as far as I can tell anyway from looking at the game's tiles in Kawaks. From an artistic standpoint, it seems like it would be much easier, as you could just about forget about palettes and the 16x16 attribute grid. It'd probably be more difficult to implement though as well as eating more graphics bandwidth.

		

